    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bolts on which the shafts have barbs or sharp projections oriented toward the head of the bolt, and that prevent the bolt from being withdrawn once set.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
